This directory contains files derived from the Pathfinder 2e system for
Foundry Virtual Tabletop (https://github.com/foundryvtt/pf2e), used under
the Apache License 2.0.

Files (and their upstream source):

  tokens.css
    Color palette and font-family variables transcribed from:
      src/styles/_colors.scss
      src/styles/_fonts.scss
    We keep a subset — the core palette, rarity, proficiency rank, and
    degree-of-success tokens — and expose them through Tailwind 4's
    @theme block so utilities like `bg-pf-primary` compile against
    var(--color-pf-primary).

  fonts.css
    Loads Google Fonts equivalents of the families referenced in
    pf2e's _fonts.scss. pf2e bundles these via Foundry's asset tree;
    we use Google Fonts for now and will revisit self-hosting if/when
    the SPA splits out of the monorepo.

No Pathfinder 2e / Paizo intellectual property is reproduced here —
only the community-contributed Foundry system's styling tokens, which
are licensed under Apache-2.0. Paizo Community Use Policy continues to
govern game-rules content (which this directory does not contain).

